snippet.title: Cookie Cutter - Exclusive Gameplay Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Watch this brutally violent gameplay trailer for Cookie Cutter. Dive into a bloody adventure techno-pop-punk 2D hand-drawn Metroidvania where you play as an android on her quest for revenge. Cookie Cutter is launching soon for PC.
